title: L A N D L I N E S - Crystal Healing Vibes
content: The latest track from the Portland power-pop outfit Landlines is called "Crystal Healing Vibes" (streaming below) and it is the first single from their upcoming full-length debut. Rife with jangly guitars, catchy melodies, and an air of collegiate… (in post Portland's Landlines working on new album from The Deli Magazine.  More by this artist at )
